These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
Hobby: fishing, gardening
Job: freelancer, architect
1. Job:freelancer is in an even position##4
2. Job:architect == Hobby:gardening##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Hobby   | gardening | fishing |
| Job     | architect    | freelancer   |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
Beverage: milk, iced-tea
Sport: soccer, climbing
1. Sport:soccer is in an odd position##4
2. Beverage:iced-tea is on the left of Beverage:milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | milk        |
| Sport      | soccer  | climbing |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
Music-Genre: electronic, gospel
Nationality: colombian, nigerian
1. Nationality:colombian is in an odd position##4
2. Music-Genre:gospel is on the left of Music-Genre:electronic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| Music-Genre   | gospel    | electronic |
| Nationality   | colombian | nigerian |

