.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-4::.
Beverage: fanta, milk
Food: strawberry, watermelon
1. Beverage:milk is on the right of Beverage:fanta##1
2. Food:watermelon is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |
| Beverage   | fanta      | milk |
| Food       | strawberry | watermelon    |

